  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study assesses static and dynamic cerebrovascular autoregulation daily over
      one week in patients with traumatic brain injury or intracranial hemorrhage to quantify the
      temporal profile of the autoregulatory status.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
